results.title: The Spawn of Sligguth
results.description: Ethan Stoddard asks help for fiancee who has fallen prey to cult of Sligguth in Starksboro. Ancient One warns Strange of Cosmic Obscenity that slumbers. Strange is overcome by Sligguth's worshippers.

results.title: In Manhattan, They Play For Keeps
Swords And Sorcery Beyond The Stars! Man-Wolf Is Back! Savagely Fighting The Otherwar!
The Lurker in the Labyrinth
results.description: Strange escapes being sacrificed to Sligguth, learns of the slumbering evil of Shuma-Gorath. Ancient One, weakened from giving power to Strange, is carried away by Shadowmen of sunken Kaa-U.

results.title: Doctor Who and the Iron Legion
The Shambler from the Sea
results.description: Strange kills Sligguth, which wakens Shambler from the Sea, N'Gabthoth. Clea and Wong are overcome by Starksboro cult. Strange frees them from sacrifice to N'Gabthoth, and discovers map of Stonehenge.

results.title: Hello, Goodbye, Hello (or, "Who's Coming and Who's Going")
The Shadows of the Starstone!
results.description: Henry Gordon inherits Witch House in England and discovers uncle's occult library. He finds sunken Kalumesh, and is attacked by demon Dagoth.  Starstone comes to life, from which writhes evil matter.

results.title: The Doom that Bloomed on Kathulos!
The Doom that Bloomed on Kathulos
results.description: Strange battles demons at Stonehenge, and is transported to living planet Kathulos.  Strange slays the plant/planet, and is marooned far from Earth.

results.title: The Crypts of Kaa-U!
results.description: Strange finds essence of Shuma-Gorath, whose trail leads to crypts of Kaa-U, where Ancient One has gone to die. A.O. saves Strange from attack of Shadowmen, & Shuma-Gorath emerges from A.O.'s mind.
